title: Minkah Gets Paid
description:
Laura Rutledge and the NFL Live Crew discuss Lamar Jacksons’ comments on his contract negotiations, the Cardinals’ long term plan with Hollywood Brown, Joe Burrow’s comments on Jessie Bates III’s contract, and Minkah Fitzpatrick becomes the highest paid Safety in the NFL.
